latestPosts.caption:
So many trials. So many beautiful options. So many hours of fittings, reworks, and brainstorming.
@dasha.uae didn’t just make an outfit — she crafted a journey ❤️❤️

From multiple outfit ideas to countless trials (we actually lost count at one point 😅), each piece was a work of art. And after all that, we finally found the one for the red carpet. 

I cannot miss to mention the efforts and constant support of my styling team and head stylist @junejasanchi who worked day and night for past 4 months to get the perfect look . 

This moment is not just about fashion — it’s about effort, creativity, and the joy of finally seeing it all come together. 

Thank you @dasha.uae and @junejasanchi for having my back and making sure u look perfect on the red carpet ❤️

#RedCarpetReady #BehindTheLook #DashaDesigner #OutfitTrials #WorthIt
